<mvc:View
controllerName="sap.ui.CrudSap.Controller.delete"
xmlns="sap.m"
xmlns:form="sap.ui.layout.form"
xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc">
	<Page class="sapUiSmallMargin"
		title="{i18n>DeletarTelaTitulo}"
		showNavButton="true"
		navButtonPress=".onNavBack">
		<Panel headerText="{i18n>DeletarTela}" class="sapUiResponsiveMargin" width="auto">
			<form:SimpleForm id="inClient" editable="false" layout="ResponsiveGridLayout">
				<Label text="Id" labelFor="id"/>
				<Input
                    id="inId"
                    value="{dadosUsuario>/idClientes}"
                    class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"
                    editable="false"/>
				<Label text="Nome" labelFor="nome"/>
				<Input
					value="{dadosUsuario>/nomeClientes}"
                    id="inNome"
                    placeholder="Nome cliente"
                    class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"
					editable="false"/>
				<Label text="Idade" labelFor="idade" />
				<Input
					value="{dadosUsuario>/idadeClientes}"
                    id="inIdade"
                    type="Number"
                    placeholder="Idade ex:21"
                    class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"
					editable="false"/>
			</form:SimpleForm>
			<Button
                    icon="sap-icon://delete"
					type="Negative"
                    text="{i18n>BtnDeletar}"
                    press=".onDeleteCliente"/>
			<Button
							type="Reject"
							icon="sap-icon://decline"
							text="{i18n>BtnCancel}"
							press=".onNavBack"/>

		</Panel>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>